{"meta":{"title":"Moroni 2","canonicalUrl":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/2?lang=eng","contentType":"text/html","audio":[{"mediaUrl":"https://media2.ldscdn.org/assets/scriptures/the-book-of-mormon-another-testament-of-jesus-christ/2015-11-2310-moroni-02-female-voice-64k-eng.mp3","voice":{"name":"female"}},{"mediaUrl":"https://media2.ldscdn.org/assets/scriptures/the-book-of-mormon-another-testament-of-jesus-christ/2015-11-2310-moroni-02-male-voice-64k-eng.mp3","voice":{"name":"male"}}],"pageAttributes":{"data-asset-id":"c528b9ff04433774f8e0ccd008b533bfe32b89cb","data-aid":"128358123","data-aid-version":"6","data-content-type":"chapter","data-uri":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/2","lang":"eng","data-orig-id":"c528b9ff04433774f8e0ccd008b533bfe32b89cb","xmlns:xsi":"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance"}},"content":{"head":{"page-meta-social":{"pageMeta":{"title":"Moroni 2","description":"Jesus gave the twelve Nephite disciples power to confer the gift of the Holy Ghost. About A.D. 401–21."},"pageSocial":{"title":"Moroni 2","description":"Jesus gave the twelve Nephite disciples power to confer the gift of the Holy Ghost. About A.D. 401–21."}},"links":[{"type":"array","rel":"stylesheet","orig-type":"text/css","href":"css/style_classic-scripture.css"}],"scripts":[]},"body":"<header>\n<p class=\"title-number\" data-aid=\"128358124\" id=\"title_number1\">Chapter 2</p>\n<p class=\"study-summary\" data-aid=\"128358125\" id=\"study_summary1\">Jesus gave the twelve Nephite disciples power to confer the gift of the Holy Ghost. About <small>A.D.</small> 401–21.</p>\n</header>\n<div class=\"body-block\">\n<span class=\"page-break\" data-page=\"519\"></span>\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"128358126\" id=\"p1\"><span class=\"verse-number\">1 </span>The words of Christ, which he spake unto his <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note1a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>disciples</a>, the twelve whom he had chosen, as he laid his hands upon them—</p>\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"128358127\" id=\"p2\"><span class=\"verse-number\">2 </span>And he called them by name, saying: Ye shall <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note2a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>call</a> on the Father in my name, in mighty prayer; and after ye have done this ye shall have <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note2b\"><sup class=\"marker\">b</sup>power</a> that to him upon whom ye shall lay your <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note2c\"><sup class=\"marker\">c</sup>hands</a>, <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note2d\"><sup class=\"marker\">d</sup>ye</a> shall give the Holy Ghost; and in my name shall ye give it, for thus do mine apostles.</p>\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"128358128\" id=\"p3\"><span class=\"verse-number\">3 </span>Now Christ spake these words unto them at the time of his first appearing; and the multitude heard it not, but the disciples heard it; and on as many as they <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note3a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>laid</a> their hands, fell the Holy Ghost.</p>\n</div>\n<footer class=\"study-notes\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"chapter\">\n<li data-marker=\"2\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"verse\">\n<li data-marker=\"1\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note1a\" data-full-marker=\"1a\">\n<p data-aid=\"128358129\" id=\"note1a_p1\"><span data-note-category=\"cross-ref\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/13.25?lang=eng#p25\">3 Ne. 13:25</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/15.11?lang=eng#p11\">15:11</a>.</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"2\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note2a\" data-full-marker=\"2a\">\n<p data-aid=\"128358130\" id=\"note2a_p1\"><span data-note-category=\"cross-ref\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/gen/4.26?lang=eng#p26\">Gen. 4:26</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/ether/4.15?lang=eng#p15\">Ether 4:15</a>.</span></p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"b\" id=\"note2b\" data-full-marker=\"2b\">\n<p data-aid=\"128358131\" id=\"note2b_p1\"><span data-note-category=\"cross-ref\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/nt/matt/10.1?lang=eng#p1\">Matt. 10:1</a>. </span><span data-note-category=\"tg\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/tg/priesthood-melchizedek?lang=eng\"><small>TG</small> Priesthood, Melchizedek</a>.</span></p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"c\" id=\"note2c\" data-full-marker=\"2c\">\n<p data-aid=\"128358132\" id=\"note2c_p1\"><span data-note-category=\"tg\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/tg/hands-laying-on-of?lang=eng\"><small>TG</small> Hands, Laying on of</a>.</span></p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"d\" id=\"note2d\" data-full-marker=\"2d\">\n<p data-aid=\"128358133\" id=\"note2d_p1\"><span data-note-category=\"cross-ref\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/18.37?lang=eng#p37\">3 Ne. 18:37</a>.</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"3\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note3a\" data-full-marker=\"3a\">\n<p data-aid=\"128358134\" id=\"note3a_p1\"><span data-note-category=\"cross-ref\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/nt/acts/19.6?lang=eng#p6\">Acts 19:6</a>.</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</footer>","associated":{"p1":[{"sizes":"250px","alt":"The Gift of the Holy Ghost","aspectRatio":"0.6666666666666666","height":"480","width":"320","missingAsset":"false","assetId":"8e69acda5ab2b8d3a856e4397c574500984fd277","srcset":"https://assets.ldscdn.org/45/b8/45b82cd654d20eb44f4cf443d1fa3579aaf73212/girl_being_confirmed.jpeg 60w,https://assets.ldscdn.org/11/d2/11d2be5412ff4da00064b0aafa623543f4a33c40/girl_being_confirmed.jpeg 100w,https://assets.ldscdn.org/35/08/35089306a99a1a2ab76ca53d06901937a867f6ee/girl_being_confirmed.jpeg 200w,https://assets.ldscdn.org/6c/e8/6ce85734371a445c93d5122dfa82803d2acd2a15/girl_b